The repository contains my dotfiles and some other configuration files.

Xdefaults:
	My .Xdefaults configuration.
	It contains my urxvt appearance and behaviour theming and
	my xscreensaver lock dialog theme.
	The urxvt color theme is based on the zenburn theme.
	
zshrc:
	My .zshrc configuration.
	Configuration files are localted under the .zsh folder.
	* Prompt theming with vcs_info and colors